        "exact": "At the pinned revision, the repository contains repeated mechanisms for eliciting and persisting practice profiles, matter histories, fallback positions, escalation matrices, deviations, and attorney rationales. The review covered 315 files and 49,365 lines, followed by per-record adjudication of 1,212 generated-pattern matches. The result establishes a static design for customer-specific adaptation and reusable local policy. Static source inspection cannot establish which components are deployed, what a tenant supplies, what leaves customer custody, or how a hosted runtime processes retained metadata.",
